375854.bio: I was born and raised in Buffalo, NY, before moving out to New York City. Growing up, I would spend a fair amount of weekends at the local dirt track, and eventually found myself occasionally working on a pit crew for a dirt street stock team. Even though I'm in the concrete jungle of NYC, I get my racing fix through iRacing, where I jump pretty freely between asphalt & dirt ovals, but I dabble in the dirt road Pro 4 trucks as well.
